{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_01","textHome":"我叫若菜纺。请多多关照—！呐，我肚子饿了@，去吃点什么吧。我知道很多好吃的店哦。@日本料理也好，西餐也好，中华料理也好，@啊，甜的东西也不错。那么那么，要去哪家@店呢？不管要吃哪家我都能给你带路哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_17","textHome":"不管是挑战性的料理，还是失败了的料理，我@都非常喜欢。不可思议的味道和口感…让我@感觉到了料理无限的可能性！@@"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_18","textHome":"到现在为止吃过的店铺的信息和回忆，全部都@记录在这个笔记本上！从小时候就开始记录@积累了，是我的宝物…！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_19","textHome":"不吃光光的话厨师先生会很伤心的哦—！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302400,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_20","textHome":"兴趣是吃，特长也是吃！我要吃到极致！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_21","textHome":"如果在网络上发表评论的话，就能给店铺做宣@传…如果在我的支援下，能救活哪怕一家好@吃却将要倒闭的餐厅就好了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302400,"motion":400}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_22","textHome":"所谓吃，就是品尝料理人的人生。料理中包含@了料理人的努力和想法以及各种各样的东西@…。我想成为将那样出色的料理和大家连接@在一起的桥梁！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":302400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_23","textHome":"我觉得我是个幸福的人。虽然我不擅长学习和@运动，但是我清楚的知道自己最重要的事情@！品尝料理，说出感想…那就是我的幸福，@我敢如此断言！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_24","textHome":"等我一下啊—！来，去吃点什么吧。料理嘛，@虽然一个人吃也可以，但是一起吃的话会更@好吃！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"id":302400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_25","textHome":"早上好—。早餐吃了什么？我吃的—…是妈妈@的特制早餐！虽然可能做得有点急，焦了一@点…不过焦了地方也很好吃"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":302400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_26","textHome":"哇，便当盒里装着各种各样的菜…好可爱—！@…嗯？稍等一下，我现在正在进行吃午饭的@意向训练"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":300}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_02","textHome":"我是若菜纺！兴趣爱好是吃！我最喜欢的就是@去各种各样的店里品尝美食。同时也写了评@论，来看看吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_27","textHome":"晚饭前的时间是最难熬的……肚子饿了的话，@就会觉得已经不行了…呜，饭还没好吗…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"id":302400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":302400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302400}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_28","textHome":"睡觉前吃东西会胖，那绝对是骗人的！因为我@即使吃了夜宵体重也没有增加啊！啊，但、@但是体重是秘密哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":302400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":302400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":302400,"motion":400}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_29","textHome":"吃太多了…没、没那回事！真的哦！我只在早@饭、零食、午饭、零食、零食、晚饭和夜宵@的时候吃东西！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":302400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302400,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_30","textHome":"趁现在吃点什么吧…饿着肚子可不能和魔女战@斗啊。啊唔啊唔啊唔啊唔啊唔…嗯？我分你@一点吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":302400,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":302400,"lipSynch":1}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302400,"lipSynch":1,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3024_00_31","textHome":"哇，那边有一个和我长得一模一样的人…喂喂@，可以跟我聊一下吗？你可能会知道我不知@道的店！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302400,